  ('generalpolice-94737317-moex-00164', 'generalpolice-94737317', 'generalpolice-94737317-moex-113-9b499a9f', 'sub-generalpolice-94737317-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '在一均勻的電場E中，有一質量為m的正電荷q以初速v向上運動，如圖所示。若電場大小足夠使 得電子無法撞到上方的正電板，且不計重力，則電荷上升至最高點所需的時間為何？', '["mv/qE", "qE/mv", "mE/qv", "qv/mE"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:27:46+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "76c106573e8e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0584ea26d335", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113060", "c": "402", "s": "1406", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "普通物理學概要與普通化學概要", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試警察人員考試、一般警察人員考試、國家安全情報人員考試、移民行政人員考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "generalpolice", "civil_category": "消防警察人員"}'::jsonb, NULL),
